{"tid":122583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【非曲線】強烈支持警方選擇性執法!!!!","createTime":"2017-02-16T06:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T03:35:28.000Z","uid":41954,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8b64558dd27768137c2ad75ff14ad3ba2e351af1","tid":122583,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T06:40:41.000Z","msg":"睇住高登仔連登仔日日屌黑警選擇性執法<br />\n警長女姦男殺論就唔查都無人查<br />\n後生仔用電腦做乜都入你萬能KEY不誠實使用電腦拉人封屋<br />\n<br />\n但奇怪每當有後生仔比警察選擇性執法既時候<br />\n高登/連燈仔單單九成留言都係抵死前抵死後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完美表現香港人核心精神第一條<br />\n睇人仆街最開心既核心價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝗蟲最多都係見到同類仆街冷血見死不救<br />\n香港人仲賤過蝗蟲<br />\n將你仆街片段重播再重播 圍住你細聲講大聲笑<br />\n見到自己人仆街有錢執咁款<br />\n然後就屌警方執法不公<br />\n乜都假 最緊要有花生食左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以話香港得老人輩一仆街?<br />\n後生長江後浪推前浪啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人點解唔抵比人選擇性執法?<br />\n踢哂腳支持啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最緊要就唔好燒埋自己果瓣就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港人根本就好應該比人選擇性執法<br />\n本身就係全民皆賤既垃圾人種<br />\n警察都係香港人 點解唔可以選擇性拉你班港畜?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n身為仆街既你有乜理由唔強烈支持警方選擇性執法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲屌人警犬前黑警後<br />\n笑撚死人真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e6f4d902188dffa891f0a01c9949f7562a7c43","tid":122583,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T06:41:44.000Z","msg":"支那狗死番支那啦"},{"pid":"b759eca4cf7a25ca932f63860ee4c9aec02a534c","tid":122583,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T06:42:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那狗死番支那啦</blockquote><br />\n唉唷唷 講中痛處又叫人返支那囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你仲賤撚過支那狗啊港畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2907988e9fac01cb34cd0168fb965ca52480ee29","tid":122583,"uid":41954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T06:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81fa3b6d9a95590b467187da934d4c6bfb550fbf","tid":122583,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:35:28.000Z","msg":"TL DR"}]}